Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your premier bowling alley. My name is Jessica. How may I assist you today?

Hi Jessica, I'm having some trouble understanding my recent billing statement.

I’d be happy to help with that. Could I first have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Alex Thompson.

Thank you, Alex. Could you please provide me with your account number so I can look up your billing details?

Of course, the account number is two three four five six seven.

Great, thank you. Now I just need to verify the last four digits of the phone number associated with the account.

Sure, the last four digits are five eight nine zero.

Thank you for the information, Alex. Please hold on for a moment while I look up your billing statement.

Okay, I've got your details here. It seems like there was an error in the last billing cycle. I will correct it and ensure a credit is applied to your next bill.

Thank you so much for your help, Jessica.

You're welcome, Alex. Thank you for your patience. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
